<span class="postbody">I saw this spell listed as new on Lucy and thought it looks like a change to charm on test?
<br />

<br />
Meddler's Misfortune 
<br />

<br />
1:  Increase Spell Resist Rate by 100% 
<br />
2:  Limit: Resist(Magic allowed) 
<br />
3:  Decrease Magic Resist by 200 
<br />
4:  Decrease 1H Slashing Damage Modifier by 50% 
<br />
5:  Increase 1H Slashing Minimum Damage Modifier by 50% 
<br />
6:  Decrease 2H Slashing Damage Modifier by 50% 
<br />
7:  Increase 2H Slashing Minimum Damage Modifier by 50% 
<br />
8:  Increase Curse Counter by 10 
<br />

<br />
Duration: 15.0 mins
<br />

<br />
 <img src="images/smiles/eusa_boohoo.gif" alt="eusa_boohoo.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
