<br />
Fair point but the rest of the information points very very strongly to a Mob cast spell not a PC spell.
<br />

<br />
There is a lot of outdated and redundant stuff on Lucy that trickles out into Allakhazam and Magelo. The level 20 blessing spells that were used during DoN testing but never made live are classic examples of this. Because of this I never take Lucy as scripture. But saying that it is still as good as we will ever get without hacking into the SOE developers own notes and files. Generally those working at Lucy make fairly good assumptions based on a lot of experience of looking at EQ data.
<br />

<br />
For me all of the information on this spell screams NPC cast spell. It's not a difficult assumption, it's fairly obvious looking at the info that is there. I think they hit the nail on the head with Category: NPC</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
